https://miketerrill.net/2016/10/16/usb-flash-drives-uefi-and-large-wims/


1. Download windows media creation tool (MCT)
2. Download windows iso from MCT, <4gb. Usual download from microsoft web site doesn't work
3. Gparted!!!   Create FAT32 partition on USB, 6048MB, GPT, name WIN2010, label WIN2010
4. mount -o loop /media/root/DiskD/Programs/Windows/Windows10_USB.iso /media/root/CD_ROM
5. Copy Files cp -R ./*
